text: Rupert Minnett (2 September 1884 - 24 June 1974) was an Australian cricketer. He played six first-class matches for New South Wales between 1909/10 and 1914/15. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1884 births Category:1974 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers Category:Cricketers from Sydney Category:L.
